name: Bacon Life "Bacon and Bones" Bracelet
description: This handmade, unisex bracelet, is simple yet bold with the combination of bone and painted beads! Don't the red beads make you hungry? don't they remind you of bacon?! (If it's just us then, that's ok too)

name: Bacon Life "Dark Bacon Rises" Hoodie
description:
This city needs a hero, and you need some bacon!

Now available just in time for the cold weather, this hoodie comes in black with out anti-love bacon symbol on front. The drawstring is a suede material which turns into a chain connected to a pair of teeth (obviously to better chew your bacon)! Accented with metallic studs on the wrists, we love subtle boldness, and we know you do too!

Comes in Sizes S-L (Ask about larger sizes)

name: Bacon Life "Twin Wood" Bracelet
description: Bacon Life brings you an unisex wooden/bone double-band bracelet! Handmade, slide-on, and durable, it's a all-around accessory that can be worn almost all the time.

name: BaconLife "I heart Bacon" Tank
description:
Show your love for us (and Bacon..but mostly us) with this!

Perfect gift for one week anniversaries, graduations, birthdays, house warming, baby shower, prison visit, old folks home visit, doctor visit, prayer service, football games, beer runs, christenings...you get the point.

name: Bacon Life "Beykhun Face" Tank
description:
A quirky, fun, UNISEX tank, great for anything..well maybe except..thunderstorms..get yours today!

Sizes: S-XXL

(Btw Beykhun is pronounced Bacon!)

name: Bacon Life "Flowchart" Tee
description:
Finally for purchase! For those who have trouble deciding a no-brainer

Comes in sizes: S - 3XL

Available in Gold (Yellow), Navy, Black, Slate (Grey)

name: Bacon Life "Bacon Hearted" Tank
description:
Finally for sale..on sale!

Unisex tank top, taking pre orders for reverse colors (Black on White)

To pre-order, choose the Pre-order option during check out.


Sizes: S-XXL

name: Bacon Life "Simply Bacon" T-Shirt
description:
A shirt for any bacon lover. Old, young, enthusiasts, even..dare we say it....Turkey Bacon lovers can enjoy the simple joy of bacon with this tee!

Let everyone know your passion! We have Men's, Women's and Kids sizes!

description:
This retro, vibrant sweatshirt oozes awesomeness..and bacon grease.

No bacon was harmed in the making of this product!

name: Boston Chery Apparel "Cheetah" Tee
description:
The official apparel for DJ Boston Chery has arrived!

Classic cut & pre-shrunk, you can rep your favorite DJ everywhere!

Comes in Black, Heather Gray, Red, and Royal Blue!

Keep up with her at www.bostonchery.com

name: Boston Chery Apparel "Cheetah" Hoodie
description:
The official apparel for DJ Boston Chery has arrived!

Lightweight, and comfortable, you can rep your favorite DJ everywhere!

Comes in Black, Red, and Royal Blue

Keep up with her at www.bostonchery.com

name: Panzell Jewelry "You're a Bloody Star" Earrings
description: Very cool. Measures two inches long.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Swimming Upstream" Earrings
description: These earrings channel the romantic feeling you get when thinking about the ocean deep under. They were created in the chandelier style, with the usage of fine gold chains and fish inspired charms, which compliment the richness of turquoise stones. When these beauties flash on your ear, one imagines the fin of a blue and gold fish in the sunlight underwater.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Lightning Storm" Earrings
description: A mix of gold and silver metal, along with some mint colored jade. The real seller are the cute lightning bolts dangling below the clouds. Abstract, cool, compliment catcher. Earrings hang 1 1/2 inches.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Thunderpussy" Earrings
description:
Feel the female fierceness of the pussycat. Yeah, feel it.

Earrings are 2 1/2'' long.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Minty Bib" Necklace
description:
Super pretty are the words that describe this piece. A mint opalescent jade pairs wonderfully with the gold and brass elements of this necklace.
Hangs around the breastbone.

name: Black Book Nine "Women's Faces of Royalty" Tee
description: The awesome Faces of Royalty Design talored for women's eyes!

name: Black Book Nine "Faces of Royalty" Tank
Black Book Nine "Faces of Royalty" Tee
description:
Take a dip into the creative world of Black Book Nine with this tee!

Men's Tee is in Maroon!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Marbled Blue Ring"
description: Comes with an adjustable band that caters to ring sizes 5-9.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Hopping Through The Looking Glass"
description:
This brass bunny is in for a whole new world after hopping through the looking glass, if you're familiar with Alice's adventures, think of the ones this bunny is in store for.
Wormholes are too cool.

Ring band is adjustable, will fit ring sizes 5-9!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Peacock Pyrite Chunk Pendant"
description: Such a pretty thing hanging from your neck! The pendant itself is about 1inch in diameter. Comes with a silver color ball chain that is 18'' long.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Peacock Pyrite Chunk Ring"
description:
These rocks are too beautiful, and you will absolutely love the way they catch light in the sun. Love love love this one!
Ring band is adjustable and caters to sizes 5-9.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Zebra Charmed"
description: A beautiful tibetan silver charm in the shape of a zebra, hanging from an 18'' silver chain. Simple but cute!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Zebra Triangle Earring"
description: Triangles are flattering against a woman's face, because the straight lines contrast so well with the face's natural curves. The zebras are an added fun touch, along with some lava rock and dalmatian jasper.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Rainbow Sprinkles Ring"
description:
Made with real sprinkles, which are sealed in with layer upon layer of enamel! Very colorful, very cute.
The band on this ring is adjustable and caters to ring sizes 5-9.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Two Toned Tube Chain"
description: Gold tubes suspended on an 18'' silver chain. Very simple and very beautiful. It's the perfect piece to throw on when you need a sweet accent to an outfit.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Pink Brass Bracelet"
description: I just love the shade of pink in these beads, can't stop using them! The band of this bracelet is brass chain and gold tubes interlinked. Closes with a lobster clasp.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Blue Egyptian Eyes Earrings"
description: Each earring is hammered to achieve an ancient look. The focal bead is a beautiful deep blue with gold veining. Earrings hang from french hooks and measures approximately two inches.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Super Tube Chain"
description: A Large Brass Tube suspended on 18'' brass ball chain. The result is a simple statement necklace that will spice up any outfit.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Goldfish's Bounty Bracelet"
description:
Ocean inspired, this bracelet has detailed fishies lined up in a row, along with stones of different blue colors. It's very pretty.
Length 7 inches.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Bast Egyptian Cat Goddess Earrings"
description:
Fun Fact: Bast was the name of a the feline deity in ancient Egyptian religion. It is assumed that the significance of the cat in Egypt was equal to that of the the cow in India.

These lovely earrings are a modest 1 1/2" inches long but they are oh so eye catching! Delicate and light, this will make any cat lady feel like a cat goddess.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Red Spike Earrings"
description: The contrast of turquoise and red coral just compete with each other since each color is so bold and beautiful. These earrings are a statement on your ears, and the delicate gold chain adds movement and channels my Indian inspiration.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Elephant Jungle Cuff"
description: This listing is for one brass cuff. The length is 6inches but it's adjustable to fit your wrist. You gotta love the texture on this metal!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Stars and Spikes Bracelet"
description: A delicate piece of work, this bracelet balances both cuteness and edginess. Every segment is given great detail. This bracelet is 7 inches long and closes with a hammered toggle clasp.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Turquoise Kali Earrings"
description: This earring is a real beauty when dangling from your ear. It incorporates a modern architectural look with Indian influences, hence the name Kali who is the Hindu goddess of the universe.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Turquoise Spike Bamboo Necklace"
description:
If you're in a hurry in the morning, this necklace will be perfect for you. It adds an edgy "pop!" to your wardrobe. Its made with elastic thread so no need to worry about those pesky clasps and toggles, just slip it over your head and tada!
Circumference is 18", so it will be slightly below the collarbone.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Pyrite Chunk Adjustable Ring"
description:
Pyrite has a very distinct look from other minerals, due to its gray metallic sheen which tends to catch light from different angles depending on the mineral formation in each piece. It looks very cool. This ring has an adjustable band in a beautiful filigree bronze color which delicately compliments the harsh industrial look of the pyrite rocks.

Adjustable band will fit ring sizes that are 5 to 10

name: Panzell Jewelry "Big Black Wolf" Ring
description:
There's something dark and dominating that emanates from this powerful predator, and if you tend to feel like this animal, well this might just be the ring for you. This wolf-tastic ring will bring a lot of attention to your hands and the finishing gives it a rich, dark, lacquered look.

The wolf head is about an inch in width and height.
Please include your ring size =]

name: Panzell Jewelry "Turquoise Scallop Spike"
description: Panzell's signature scallop look with beautiful turquoise hues. These are sure to get attention.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Zebra Tribe Bracelet"
description: A very earthy bracelet. There's a bit of polished pyrite, gold filigree, spotted jasper, and wood. It all looks great together!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Hipster Owl Chain"
description:
The owl, always silently judging you, its on the rage with hipsters. Each piece is carefully molded, baked and painted. Comes with a 24'' inch bronze ball chain.
He's watching.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Turquoise Skulled Bracelet"
description:
This will look so pretty on your wrist. The colors just pop against each other, the skulls give it an edge and the dangling accents gives it a feminine flirtiness.
Bracelets are stretchy so they go on and come off easily.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Pale Pink Spike Dangle"
description:
These are sooo cute! I love this shade of pink because it reminds me of cherry blossoms, so pretty when paired with the gold and spike.
You'll love these!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Vertical Rosy Pink & Gold" Ring
description: There's something so delicately feminine about the soft shade of pink in this ring, without being overpoweringly girly.

name: Panzell Jewerly "Bronze Skull Trio" Bracelet
description:
Yeah they're a little scary but they're also so cute! Grab yourself a wristful of these guys and show your friends how cool you are.

Each bracelet circumference is 7inches which fits around the average wrist.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Turquoise Spike Dangle"
description: Turquoise is still in! Grab these simple beauties which will compliment any outfit.

name: Panzell Jewelry "Black Cloisonne Spike Dangle"
description: Oh la la love these! They're just like the Turquoise Cloisonne Spike Dangle, but the black color makes it romantic and daring. Great for the nightlife!

name: Panzell Jewelry "Rosy Pink Gold Studs" Earrings
description: Grab these cute little studs that will remind you of those blossoming cherry blossoms against the sunlit sky. The stud post is suitable for a 20 gauge ear piercing, which is the size of all earring hooks.

name: Black Book Nine "Monster, Men & Madness" Tank
